data.description: Welcome to the perfect starter home. Conveniently located off of Hwy 90 & Beltway 8, only 15 minutes from Downtown Houston. Gated property with an over 6,000 sqft lot, located on a cul-de-sac street meaning minimal traffic. This home offers 3 bedrooms, 1.5 bathrooms, formal living & dining room, as well as a breakfast nook. This freshly painted Spanish-Modern home, is waiting for you!
